@coralgardeners founder @toutiess is on a mission to revive the ocean’s coral reefs worldwide, with the support of our Perpetual Planet Initiative. Determined to prove that nothing is impossible in ocean restoration, he has welcomed fellow member of the Rolex family of Testimonees @dr.sylviaearle to the team’s newly launched Thailand branch, a vital ecosystem that could become a Mission Blue Hope Spot.
#Rolex #PerpetualPlanet #Reachforthecrown
