Still buzzing with inspiration after a beautiful night at the Red Sea Film Festival celebrating women in cinema 🤍💫

Representation in film matters. When girls and women see themselves on screen, it opens their eyes to what’s possible - it sparks dreams, expands horizons, and changes the narrative. As @oprah said, “You can’t be what you can’t see.” That visibility empowers imagination and belief. So thank you @redseafilm for championing these stories - it’s powerful, it’s necessary, and it’s shaping the future.

And deep gratitude to @jomanaalrashid, Faisal and Shivani for leading with vision, intention, and heart - and for uplifting the next generation of storytellers 🙌🏽 

@chopard 
@rachelgilbertau @danixmichelle
@renatocampora
@ivangomez 
@ranifawazofficial 

#WomenInCinema #RedSealFF #RedSeaFilmFoundation #Cannes
